text: Kitchel is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Cornelius P. Kitchel (1875–1947), former mayor of Englewood, New Jersey * Denison Kitchel (1908–2002), campaign manager of Barry M. Goldwater * Harvey Denison Kitchel (1812–1895), former president of Middlebury College * Jane Kitchel (born 1945), member of the Vermont Senate * Ted Kitchel (born 1959), basketball player ==See also== * Kitchel, Indiana, an unincorporated community in Union County * Kitchell, surname
